title: Tiffany Sessions // 181
description:
In 1989, a 20-year-old woman headed out for a late afternoon power walk in Florida and didn’t come home. After conducting the largest search in Alachua County history, investigators concluded that she was likely the victim of a serial killer. This is the story of Tiffany Sessions.
